&gt; 
&gt; being blocked by negative entities. 
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; I only one of a few that have gotten this exact communication. So 
&gt; 
&gt; there is a real threat from negative energy or entities.
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; Plus through research we have found that it is possible for entities 
&gt; 
&gt; to travel back and forth between our realms during an open box 
&gt; 
&gt; session. If you listened to numerous files Steve and I have posted 
&gt; 
&gt; asking our friends mike and Lisa on the other side to insure that all 
&gt; 
&gt; and any spirits that may have traveled through please go back and 
&gt; 
&gt; have gotten conformation from them every time.
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; If it is possible for an entity to travel through the portal that a 
&gt; 
&gt; box MAY produce then it stands to reason it is possible that it can 
&gt; 
&gt; be a dark entity.
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; As far as fear goes, I agree wholeheartedly, fear definitely feeds 
&gt; 
&gt; the negative. And that is my point. The protection ritual does not 
&gt; 
&gt; create a relative tangible barrier, it is simply a metaphoric symbol 
&gt; 
&gt; of putting your mind in the right place so as not to feed this 
&gt; 
&gt; negative energy.
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; And the protection we receive from our tech/guides on the other side 
&gt; 
&gt; in my belief is very real, I believe they do actually run 
&gt; 
&gt; interference for us as far as negativity goes and the part of the 
&gt; 
&gt; ritual where we invoke their help is just a form of respect and 
&gt; 
&gt; acknowledgement that they are constantly watching out for us.
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; this being said, Of course everyone will adhere to their own beliefs 
&gt; 
&gt; as far as this subject is concerned. I just felt that your response 
&gt; 
&gt; was a little strong and came more from the attitude that I also 
&gt; 
&gt; suffer from that is to say &quot; negative spirit yeah bring it on&quot;
